<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.3.4">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://tevinzhang.com/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="https://tevinzhang.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2024-10-16T17:33:21+08:00</updated><id>https://tevinzhang.com/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Tevin Zhang</title><subtitle></subtitle><author><name>Tevin Zhang</name><email>hey(at)tevinzhang(dot)com</email></author><entry xml:lang="zh"><title type="html">我如何管理了 12 年的笔记</title><link href="https://tevinzhang.com/zh/notes-over-12-years" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="我如何管理了 12 年的笔记" /><published>2024-08-23T00:00:00+08:00</published><updated>2024-09-25T21:48:10+08:00</updated><id>https://tevinzhang.com/zh/notes-over-12-years</id><author><name>Tevin Zhang</name><email>hey(at)tevinzhang(dot)com</email></author><category term="blog" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[我有一个从2012年开始的Git仓库。在那之前，我记得使用Notational Velocity1和一堆文本文件，它运行得很好，直到我决定将我的笔记保留一辈子。如果我没有将它们数字化，我会在索引卡上写笔记，并将它们存放在盒子里进行组织。只要我能保存这些盒子，我就能保留我的笔记。 Notational Velocity 是一个让我快速搜索和切换文件的文本编辑器。后来我转用了nvALT，这是Notational Velocity的一个分支，增加了一些额外功能和界面修改，包括MultiMarkdown功能。 ↩]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry xml:lang="en"><title type="html">How I’ve managed notes over 12 years</title><link href="https://tevinzhang.com/notes-over-12-years" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="How I’ve managed notes over 12 years" /><published>2024-08-15T00:00:00+08:00</published><updated>2024-09-25T21:48:10+08:00</updated><id>https://tevinzhang.com/notes-over-12-years</id><author><name>Tevin Zhang</name><email>hey(at)tevinzhang(dot)com</email></author><category term="blog" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[I have a Git repository dating back to 2012. Before that, I remember using Notational Velocity1 with a bunch of text files, it worked well, until I decided to keep my notes for life. If I’m not digitizing them, I’ll write notes on index cards and store them in boxes for organizing. As long as I can keep the boxes, I get to keep my notes. Notational Velocity is a text editor that lets me quickly search and switch between files. Later I switched to nvALT—a fork of Notational Velocity with some additional features and interface modifications, including MultiMarkdown functionality. ↩]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry xml:lang="zh"><title type="html">家用小型管理交换机对比</title><link href="https://tevinzhang.com/zh/home-switches-comparison" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="家用小型管理交换机对比" /><published>2024-06-03T00:00:00+08:00</published><updated>2024-09-25T21:48:10+08:00</updated><id>https://tevinzhang.com/zh/home-switches-comparison</id><author><name>Tevin Zhang</name><email>hey(at)tevinzhang(dot)com</email></author><summary type="html"><![CDATA[需求是 VLAN 单线复用，不用 IPTV 但需要把弱电箱里的网口通过一根线交换到另一个房间的路由上，同时兼顾拨号。千兆交换够用，也是考虑到目前更高带宽设备的普及度和性价比后的一个更实际的选择。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry xml:lang="en"><title type="html">Home switches comparison</title><link href="https://tevinzhang.com/home-switches-comparison" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Home switches comparison" /><published>2024-06-03T00:00:00+08:00</published><updated>2024-09-25T21:48:10+08:00</updated><id>https://tevinzhang.com/home-switches-comparison</id><author><name>Tevin Zhang</name><email>hey(at)tevinzhang(dot)com</email></author><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The requirement is VLAN single-line multiplexing. Although IPTV is not needed, I need to switch the network port in the weak current box to a router in another room through a single line, while also accommodating dial-up. Gigabit switching is adequate and a more practical choice after considering the current popularity and cost effectiveness of higher bandwidth devices.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry xml:lang="en"><title type="html">Don’t humanize businesses</title><link href="https://tevinzhang.com/dont-humanize-businesses" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Don’t humanize businesses" /><published>2024-01-12T00:00:00+08:00</published><updated>2024-09-26T09:16:49+08:00</updated><id>https://tevinzhang.com/dont-humanize-businesses</id><author><name>Tevin Zhang</name><email>hey(at)tevinzhang(dot)com</email></author><category term="blog" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[To be let go for no reason is like a huge slap in the face from a company that I really wanted to believe in]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry xml:lang="zh"><title type="html">不要把企业当人看</title><link href="https://tevinzhang.com/zh/dont-humanize-businesses" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="不要把企业当人看" /><published>2024-01-12T00:00:00+08:00</published><updated>2024-09-26T09:16:49+08:00</updated><id>https://tevinzhang.com/zh/dont-humanize-businesses</id><author><name>Tevin Zhang</name><email>hey(at)tevinzhang(dot)com</email></author><category term="blog" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[无缘无故被解雇就像是被一个我真心想要相信的公司狠狠地打了一巴掌]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry xml:lang="zh"><title type="html">在OpenBSD上进行私有Git托管</title><link href="https://tevinzhang.com/zh/git-hosting" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="在OpenBSD上进行私有Git托管" /><published>2023-10-05T00:00:00+08:00</published><updated>2023-12-11T21:30:04+08:00</updated><id>https://tevinzhang.com/zh/git-hosting</id><author><name>Tevin Zhang</name><email>hey(at)tevinzhang(dot)com</email></author><summary type="html"><![CDATA[2023-12-11: 添加了第二种 clone 方式]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry xml:lang="en"><title type="html">Private git hosting on OpenBSD</title><link href="https://tevinzhang.com/git-hosting" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Private git hosting on OpenBSD" /><published>2023-10-05T00:00:00+08:00</published><updated>2023-12-11T21:30:04+08:00</updated><id>https://tevinzhang.com/git-hosting</id><author><name>Tevin Zhang</name><email>hey(at)tevinzhang(dot)com</email></author><summary type="html"><![CDATA[2023-12-11: Added an alternative way to clone]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry xml:lang="zh"><title type="html">在 Yunohost 上备份 crontabs</title><link href="https://tevinzhang.com/zh/backup-crontabs-on-yunohost" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="在 Yunohost 上备份 crontabs" /><published>2023-09-16T00:00:00+08:00</published><updated>2023-09-16T19:38:36+08:00</updated><id>https://tevinzhang.com/zh/backup-crontabs-on-yunohost</id><author><name>Tevin Zhang</name><email>hey(at)tevinzhang(dot)com</email></author><summary type="html"><![CDATA[YunoHost通常已经知道需要备份什么。但是，如果您进行了手动更改，例如在YunoHost应用程序系统之外安装了应用程序，您可能希望扩展YunoHost的机制以指定其他要备份的文件。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry xml:lang="en"><title type="html">Backup crontabs on Yunohost</title><link href="https://tevinzhang.com/backup-crontabs-on-yunohost" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Backup crontabs on Yunohost" /><published>2023-09-16T00:00:00+08:00</published><updated>2023-09-16T19:38:36+08:00</updated><id>https://tevinzhang.com/backup-crontabs-on-yunohost</id><author><name>Tevin Zhang</name><email>hey(at)tevinzhang(dot)com</email></author><summary type="html"><![CDATA[YunoHost usually already knows what needs to be backed up. However, if you have made manual changes, such as installing an app outside of the YunoHost application system, you may want to extend YunoHost’s mechanism to specify other files to be backed up.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://tevinzhang.com/assets/avatar.png" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>